summary: AN ORDINANCE in implementation of certain undertakings and covenants by the City contained in that certain agreement (GC 2894) with the State of Washington authorized by Ordinance 99662, which agreement provides for the cancellation and termination of Agreement GC 541-B relating to the construction of the Roanoke Connection and the R. H. Thomson Expressway, and making appropriations from the Seattle General Arterial Improvement Bond 1954 Fund and the Seattle General Street Improvement Bond 1960 Fund.
